Lineage and credits
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

BoardBridge modernizes, in concept, the Surface-to-OpenGL approach of Boardwalk,
a Minecraft: Java Edition launcher for Android by Zhuowei Zhang (zhuowei).

    Boardwalk
    Copyright Zhuowei Zhang and contributors
    Source:  https://github.com/zhuowei/Boardwalk
    License: Apache License, Version 2.0

Boardwalk bound an Android Surface to an OpenGL context by subclassing the
framework android.opengl.GLSurfaceView and handling the surface lifecycle via
SurfaceHolder callbacks. BoardBridge takes that concept and reimplements it as a
native ANativeWindow -> EGL -> OpenGL ES 3.2 bridge. No substantial Boardwalk
source is reproduced here; the Apache-2.0 license and this attribution are
carried forward to honor that lineage.

Portions of the original Boardwalk headers carry the following notice, which is
preserved here for attribution:

